Rating: 0
Scrambled eggs do not have to be cooked on a low heat for 25 minutes. Who has the time. The trick to creamy scrambled eggs is to gently cook them until just before they're set, remove from heat and let the heat in the pan finish cooking them. I guarantee that they will be creamy even without cheese, butter or cream.

